Project Outline
Access Control Dashboard

Purpose: Provides a centralized view of access controls across various systems, highlighting any misconfigurations or missing permissions.
Features:
Real-time monitoring of user permissions and roles.
Automated periodic reviews to detect unauthorized access.
Alerts for any high-risk configurations, such as admin accounts without MFA.
Credential Manager Tool

Purpose: Manages credential lifecycle, enforcing expiration policies, and checking for weak or reused credentials.
Features:
Automated tracking of credential expiration and alerts for renewal.
Detection of reused or weak passwords across systems.
Optional integration with password management systems or centralized authentication directories.
